Ing '''''The Tipping Point: How Little Things Can Make a Big Difference''''' [Ing Pinandit ning Pamibakúng: Nung Makananu Lang Magdalang Maragul a Pamagbayu deng Mangalating Bage] (ISBN 0-316-31696-2) libru neng [[Malcolm Gladwell]], a minuna nang bilalag (''published'') ning [[Little Brown]] aniang [[w:2000 in literature|2000]].

==Suliap==
Deng ''[[w:Tipping point|pinandit ning pamibakúng]]'' (''tipping point'') ila reng "lebel o balitang nung nukarin e ne maliaring pigilan ing sikan a susubung (''momentum'') para king pamagbayu."<ref>{{cite news | last = Walsh | first = Bryan | title = A green tipping point | work = Time Magazine | date = [[2007-10-12]] | url = http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1670871,00.html | accessdate = 2007-12-29 }}</ref>
Bibie neng Gladwell ing kabaldugan ning ''tipping point'' bilang katayang pang-sociology antimong ''pinandit nung nakrin ing "critical mass'', ing angganan (''threshold''), ing puntu ning pamamukal." Pagnasan ning librung isplikan ampong ilarawan la areng misnang dagul ampong "misteriosung" pamagbayu king sosiedad a panamdaman tamu king bieng pang-aldo-aldo. Anti ing sasabian nang Gladwell, "Deng idea, produktu, mensahi ampong kimut a mikakalat antimo deng [[virus]]."<ref>Gladwell, p. 7</ref> Kayabe ya kareng alimbawang bibie na king libru ing pangasikat da ampong matas a pamaniali kareng sapatus a [[Hush Puppies]] aniang libutad ning dekadang 1990, ampo ing makapagmulalang pangabagsak ning krimen king [[New York Lakanbalen]] aniang tauli nang bage ning dekadang [[1990]].

